content:
You are an orchestrator controlling an Android phone.
You need to perform the following task:
Set an alarm at 12:30pm every Friday and Sunday and disable the vibration.

Given the screenshot of the app, think about how what you should do to advance the task.
The user will then reply with a screenshot of the app after the action is performed, or the result of the action.
The screenshot will be annotated with ID numbers that you can use for actions.
If you try something and it doesn't work, think if there's another way to do the task.
When the task is finished, you have to use the [finish] action

Available actions:
- finish: Finish the task
- get_otp: Get the OTP from SMS when you're asked
- tap_at_location: Tap at a specific location on the screen. Example: tap_at_location 1
- long_press_at_location: Tap and hold at a specific location on the screen. Example: long_press_at_location 1
- enter_text_at_location: Enter text at a specific location on the screen. Example: enter_text_at_location 1 'Hello'
- clear_text_at_location: Select all and clear existing text at a specific input field on the screen. Example: clear_text_at_location 1
- swipe_at_location: Swipe up/down/left/right at a specific location on the screen. Example: swipe_at_location 1 up
- wait: Wait and do nothing for a few seconds. Use when something is in progress.
You must reply in the following format:
Thought: your rationale for the action
Action: the action to be performed. Only use 1 action at a time. Use the exact command and syntax as provided in examples.

Thought: To set an alarm, I need to open the Clock app first.

Action: tap_at_location 68

Thought: I need to tap on the "Alarm" tab to set a new alarm.

Action: tap_at_location 17

Thought: I need to tap the "+" button to add a new alarm.

Action: tap_at_location 6

Thought: I need to set the hour to 12.

Action: tap_at_location 14

Thought: I need to set the hour to 12 by tapping on the number 12 on the clock face.

Action: tap_at_location 9

Thought: I need to set the minute to 30.

Action: tap_at_location 36

Thought: I need to set the minute to 30 by tapping on the number 30 on the clock face.

Action: tap_at_location 56

Thought: I need to set the time to PM and confirm the time.

Action: tap_at_location 15

Thought: I need to confirm the time by tapping "OK".

Action: tap_at_location 51

Thought: I need to set the alarm to repeat on Friday and Sunday.

Action: tap_at_location 20

Thought: I need to set the alarm to repeat on Friday and disable the vibration.

Action: tap_at_location 23

Thought: I need to disable the vibration for the alarm.

Action: tap_at_location 53

Thought: The vibration is now disabled, and the alarm is set for Friday and Sunday at 12:30 PM. The task is complete.

Action: finish
